| Rate Limiting | Added `express-rate-limit` |
| Input Validation | Explicit validation with error messages |
| Error Handling | Try-catch with async handler wrapper |
| Logging | Structured logging with `morgan` |
| Payload Size | Limited to 10KB |
| Environment Config | Using `.env` file and dotenv |
| Error Disclosure | Different responses for dev/prod |
| CORS | Can be configured as needed |
| Authentication | Ready to add middleware |

